      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that\u2019s ready for all your adventures? This car has been so good to me, and it's still in really solid shape! It runs smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure it\u2019ll be a great fit for you!",
