    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example delivers an engaging analog experience via its 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its composure thanks to a well-maintained MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes a dual-VANOS system service and a comprehensive subframe inspection. While the exterior and interior exhibit a light patina consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain remains tight, providing the urgent throttle response and balanced weight distribution this platform is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Maintenance up to date. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Reliable daily driver.",
