    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presented in a striking Metallic Charcoal, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained and offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its honest highway history. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple black leather upholstery; while the driver\u2019s seat shows very light softening on the bolster, the interior remains remarkably crisp. All technological features, including the premium sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service record of synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The tires provide excellent grip with plenty of life remaining, and the brakes are firm and responsive. This is a solid, dependable car that drives as well as it looks, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
